Translation:
  Arrow Up: 		Translate Up Y
  Arrow Down: 		Translate Down Y
  Arrow Left: 		Translate Left X
  Arrow Right: 		Translate Right X
  Shift + Arrow Up: 	Translate Up Z
  Shift + Arrow Down: 	Translate Down Z

Rotation:
  w: Rotate Up
  a: Rotate Left
  s: Rotate Down
  d: Rotate Right

Rotation:
  i: Scale Increase On Y
  j: Scale Decrease On X
  k: Scale Decrease On Y
  l: Scale Increase On X
